# Transfer Entropy Analysis in the Energy Sector

This repository contains the final project submission for **COMP0047: Data Science**, as part of the **MSc Artificial Intelligence and Data Engineering** program at UCL. The project investigates directional information flow in the energy sector using **Transfer Entropy (TE)** estimated via both discrete binning and $k$-nearest neighbors (kNN) methods.

